_:Na76a86539a3f4976be85621cf3ab768f <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Contact details:</p>\n\n<p>Ministry of Defence Press Desk</p>\n\n<p>Telephone: 020 721 87907</p>\n\n<p>All other enquiries, please contact Veterans UK helpline.</p>\n\n<p>These contact details are for media enquiries only. All other enquiries should be made to our helpline facility:</p>\n\n<p>Veterans UK helpline</p>\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\nVeterans UK<br>Ministry of Defence<br>Norcross<br>Thornton-Cleveleys<br>FY5 3WP\n</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Email <a href=\"mailto:veterans-uk@mod.gov.uk%20\" class=\"govuk-link\">veterans-uk@mod.gov.uk</a></p>\n\n<p>Freephone (UK only): 0808 1914 2 18</p>\n\n<p>Telephone (overseas): +44 1253 866 043</p>\n\n<p>Our current opening hours are 8am to 4pm Monday to Friday. Please email us for enquiries outside these times.</p>\n</div>" .
